			<div class="genericPar">
				the four singers on this album are ariel levine, ross beshear, ben miller, and joe barney. thank you guys - thanks for dealing with my tediousness and working so hard on the music. ariel's band is called <a href="http://www.kindergartennyc.com" title="ariel levine's kindergarten">kindergarten</a> and ben's band is called <a href="http://www.thelowanthem.com" title="ben miller's the low anthem" >the low anthem</a>.
			</div>

			<div class="genericPar">
				<a href="http://www.billmeadmusic.com" title="bill mead music">bill mead</a> and paul mason are on drums. <a href="http://www.udilevy.com" title="udi levy's music">udi levy</a>, ariel levine, and ben miller on guitar. there is jeff prystowsky, who is also in the low anthem, on upright bass on track four. thank you to all the musicians and engineers that worked on the music. thank you jack [for all the guidance], john, ray [both of you] &amp; dave, guy &amp; sam.
